1
00:01:05,822 --> 00:01:08,254
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,382 --> 00:01:11,294
=Episode 11=

3
00:01:11,799 --> 00:01:13,719
You told me to say that to Mother today.

4
00:01:13,719 --> 00:01:14,719
You knew Prince Ning

5
00:01:14,719 --> 00:01:16,760
and the Marquis of Zhenbei
would cause trouble.

6
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:21,079
Their plans for the autumn hunt
and the Yin Yang dolls failed.

7
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:23,079
Now, Jinming is unfit for the burden.

8
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:26,319
They think I'm only good for fighting.

9
00:01:26,799 --> 00:01:29,319
So they won't let go of
this once-in-a-lifetime opportunity.

10
00:01:32,079 --> 00:01:34,560
You should wear this soft armor instead.

11
00:01:36,959 --> 00:01:38,640
They might not kill me directly.

12
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:40,239
The battlefield is dangerous.

13
00:01:40,439 --> 00:01:42,760
I'll feel more at ease if you wear it.

14
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:45,799
You wear it.

15
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:50,159
Come.

16
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,159
I have something to give you.

17
00:01:52,879 --> 00:01:54,439
What is it? So mysterious.

18
00:02:02,719 --> 00:02:05,480
We've never been apart
since you entered the palace.

19
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,959
You're going to the border
to fight for me.

20
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,520
I guess you'll miss me.

21
00:02:10,319 --> 00:02:11,240
Put it on.

22
00:02:11,479 --> 00:02:14,120
On the battlefield, it will be
as if I'm with you at all times.

23
00:02:17,439 --> 00:02:18,360
Xiao Jinyun.

24
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,560
Look.

25
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,919
Don't you look handsome in this armor?

26
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:27,520
I really wish I could wear the armor

27
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:28,759
and take the risk for you.

28
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,479
Becoming you

29
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,199
gives me the chance

30
00:02:32,319 --> 00:02:34,039
to become the one I want to be.

31
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:37,159
Ever since I was young, I've wanted

32
00:02:37,319 --> 00:02:38,240
to charge into battle

33
00:02:38,919 --> 00:02:41,520
and serve the nation
like my father and brothers.

34
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:45,719
That has been my dream since childhood.

35
00:02:46,439 --> 00:02:47,639
This is not an adventure.

36
00:02:48,439 --> 00:02:50,639
It's the best gift
Your Majesty has given me.

37
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,680
I'm not worried about you.

38
00:02:53,599 --> 00:02:56,479
I'm worried that my body
will hold you back.

39
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:59,360
Have you forgotten? I have another name.

40
00:03:05,039 --> 00:03:08,960
Father has summoned General Xu's family
to the palace for a meal again.

41
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,159
So noisy!

42
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,960
You're right.

43
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:15,580
Who's there?

44
00:03:17,639 --> 00:03:18,919
Sorry, I missed.

45
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:20,360
Trying to assassinate us?

46
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,919
I was trying to hit birds.

47
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:25,919
Their droppings
were almost on your heads.

48
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:27,080
Who are you?

49
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:28,240
Why are you here?

50
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:30,680
I came to the palace with my father.

51
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,240
But I got lost.

52
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:34,599
My name is Xu Tie.

53
00:03:34,599 --> 00:03:36,319
I'm the third son of the Xu family.

54
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,000
Easy.

55
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,319
You can play with this.

56
00:03:40,479 --> 00:03:42,080
What about you? Will you remember me?

57
00:03:42,159 --> 00:03:43,039
I am...

58
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:45,639
- Xu Tie.
- Xu Tie.

59
00:03:50,439 --> 00:03:51,159
How about this?

60
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,960
I'll take Your Majesty
to test out your body.

61
00:03:56,864 --> 00:04:02,048
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

62
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:06,120
Your Majesty.

63
00:04:06,439 --> 00:04:08,159
How long are you going
to keep holding me?

64
00:04:08,672 --> 00:04:13,960
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

65
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:17,720
I thought you were going
to do something with my body.

66
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:20,360
Why did you bring me
to such a high place?

67
00:04:21,319 --> 00:04:22,399
I want you to see

68
00:04:22,399 --> 00:04:25,319
if I can charge forward

69
00:04:25,439 --> 00:04:26,399
and fight the enemy.

70
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,079
Be careful!

71
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:33,504
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

72
00:04:33,696 --> 00:04:36,920
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

73
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,420
Come.

74
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:39,120
I'll hold your hand.

75
00:04:43,232 --> 00:04:44,992
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

76
00:04:45,312 --> 00:04:48,928
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

77
00:04:49,175 --> 00:04:53,920
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪

78
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,920
When I was little,

79
00:04:55,199 --> 00:04:58,120
my father and eldest brother
often went to battle,

80
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,600
leaving me home alone.

81
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:03,240
I would run to the roof
to look at the sky.

82
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:05,240
Because I knew

83
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:07,959
I was under the same sky as them.

84
00:05:08,519 --> 00:05:11,480
And we might be
looking at the same star.

85
00:05:18,048 --> 00:05:23,312
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

86
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:24,920
Xiao Jinyun.

87
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,519
I promise.

88
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,199
I will return safely.

89
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,639
I keep my word.

90
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:31,319
Xu Yu.

91
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:33,040
So will I.

92
00:05:34,639 --> 00:05:35,759
No doubt in us.

93
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:37,839
I keep my word.

94
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:43,200
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

95
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:47,136
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

96
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:52,079
Look, stars.

97
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,200
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

98
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:58,480
♪All who believed love would never fade♪

99
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,720
The army is assembled.

100
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,040
Waiting for Your Majesty's word.

101
00:06:04,832 --> 00:06:06,904
♪Like a song, like a dream, like a play♪

102
00:06:06,904 --> 00:06:10,859
♪This life is but a solitary boat♪

103
00:06:10,859 --> 00:06:16,850
♪No one ferries me
across this sea of pain♪

104
00:06:28,224 --> 00:06:32,973
♪Fate tears us apart♪

105
00:06:34,031 --> 00:06:43,232
♪Embrace again, hurt again, start again♪

106
00:06:43,232 --> 00:06:45,024
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

107
00:06:45,024 --> 00:06:49,440
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

108
00:06:52,319 --> 00:06:53,319
Wait for me to return.

109
00:06:54,470 --> 00:06:56,480
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

110
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,319
I'll wait for you.

111
00:07:00,416 --> 00:07:05,319
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪

112
00:07:05,319 --> 00:07:06,160
Set out!

113
00:07:06,304 --> 00:07:08,384
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

114
00:07:08,384 --> 00:07:12,704
♪All who believed love would never fade♪

115
00:07:12,704 --> 00:07:17,792
♪The wind scatters countless sorrows♪

116
00:07:17,792 --> 00:07:19,840
♪Like a song, like a dream, like a play♪

117
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:23,992
♪This life is but a solitary boat♪

118
00:07:23,992 --> 00:07:30,304
♪No one ferries me
across this sea of pain♪

119
00:08:24,279 --> 00:08:24,839
Stop.

120
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,248
Your Majesty, what's wrong?

121
00:08:30,079 --> 00:08:32,559
Why do I feel there's an ambush?

122
00:08:33,519 --> 00:08:35,039
Ambush?

123
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:21,299
Father!

124
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,759
Xu Han is here!

125
00:09:25,399 --> 00:09:26,200
(Xu Han)
Everyone!

126
00:09:26,399 --> 00:09:27,440
Kill them!

127
00:09:27,519 --> 00:09:28,759
- Kill!
- Kill!

128
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,519
(Counter thrust?)

129
00:10:10,112 --> 00:10:11,744
(Fengyi Palace)

130
00:10:39,519 --> 00:10:41,039
So this is your review work?

131
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:41,840
Do it again.

132
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,919
Or else, no dinner for you.

133
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:44,679
No, please!

134
00:10:44,679 --> 00:10:45,919
I've done it five times.

135
00:10:46,279 --> 00:10:47,720
Could you bear to see me starve?

136
00:10:52,639 --> 00:10:53,279
Your Highness.

137
00:10:53,279 --> 00:10:55,519
The Empress and Prince Xiaoyao
are alone in the garden.

138
00:10:55,519 --> 00:10:56,720
What?

139
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,320
They're arm-in-arm, so intimate!

140
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:02,440
It's barely been days
since His Majesty departed for war.

141
00:11:02,559 --> 00:11:04,639
And now, they are intimate.

142
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:10,720
The Empress's position
will finally be mine.

143
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:13,360
Congratulations in advance.

144
00:11:17,559 --> 00:11:18,336
You are rewarded.

145
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,480
Thank you.

146
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:23,559
Today, luckily, you arrived in time.

147
00:11:23,559 --> 00:11:24,879
It was close, but we're safe.

148
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:26,240
But Marshal Xu,

149
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:28,440
how did you know
about the ambush in the valley?

150
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,519
Sit and explain.

151
00:11:33,759 --> 00:11:34,480
Your Majesty,

152
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:37,799
I observed that Dada appeared quiet,

153
00:11:38,279 --> 00:11:40,879
but small squads
had been dispatched each night.

154
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:44,600
When imperial reports
confirmed Your Majesty's expedition,

155
00:11:45,039 --> 00:11:48,639
I deduced that they would
ambush you in the valley.

156
00:11:49,759 --> 00:11:52,679
(My father is always the smartest.)

157
00:11:54,799 --> 00:11:55,559
Marshal Xu,

158
00:11:55,879 --> 00:11:57,679
you're a battle-hardened general.

159
00:11:57,679 --> 00:12:00,240
You know the military inside out.

160
00:12:01,799 --> 00:12:03,000
You flatter me, Your Majesty.

161
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:04,879
Report!

162
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,200
Your Majesty,

163
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,960
we captured a man
among the fleeing enemies.

164
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:13,000
Bring him.

165
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:13,519
Yes.

166
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:16,940
Bring him!

167
00:12:30,879 --> 00:12:31,759
Who are you?

168
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:32,720
I...

169
00:12:33,159 --> 00:12:34,200
I'm a refugee.

170
00:12:34,399 --> 00:12:36,000
Those soldiers captured me

171
00:12:36,039 --> 00:12:37,200
to force me into hard labor.

172
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:39,879
Refugees never fled
to deserted wastelands.

173
00:12:39,879 --> 00:12:41,639
Your Majesty, I can tell he's a spy.

174
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:43,000
I'm not a spy!

175
00:12:43,639 --> 00:12:44,799
You saved me.

176
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,320
Let me stay with you.

177
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,840
We're heading to war.

178
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:50,279
Why bring dead weight like you?

179
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:51,960
I know some martial arts.

180
00:12:52,759 --> 00:12:53,960
I can aid you in battle.

181
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:03,840
Your Majesty.

182
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:17,200
Let's have a sparring match.

183
00:13:18,279 --> 00:13:18,960
Don't!

184
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:20,740
Release him.

185
00:13:38,879 --> 00:13:40,159
(Our family's sword technique!)

186
00:13:40,559 --> 00:13:42,360
(Yu only entered the palace a year ago.)

187
00:13:42,519 --> 00:13:43,879
(With the Emperor's physique,)

188
00:13:44,039 --> 00:13:46,000
(how is he so proficient
with this technique?)

189
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:49,320
(And that counter thrust
earlier was clearly...)

190
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:01,759
Just as I thought.

191
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,320
You're a woman!

192
00:14:23,687 --> 00:14:28,871
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

193
00:14:29,607 --> 00:14:34,170
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

194
00:14:35,495 --> 00:14:40,910
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

195
00:14:41,479 --> 00:14:46,023
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

196
00:14:46,663 --> 00:14:51,927
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

197
00:14:52,295 --> 00:14:57,972
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

198
00:14:58,311 --> 00:15:00,327
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

199
00:15:00,519 --> 00:15:04,263
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

200
00:15:04,839 --> 00:15:09,511
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

201
00:15:10,055 --> 00:15:11,815
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

202
00:15:12,135 --> 00:15:15,751
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

203
00:15:15,998 --> 00:15:21,525
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
